On Sun, 15 Feb 2009, David Schwarze wrote:

> I see it a bit differently.  Posting VW parts that one has just put on E-Bay 
> says to me, "Hey, I need to sell this stuff and I want to get top dollar for 
> it so rather than offer it up first to fellow listmembers for a reasonable 
> price, I already listed it on E-Bay and if any of you people in this blog or 
> whatever want my parts you can go bid against everyone else on the planet for 
